# Instant QR Application - Implementation Plan

The goal is to build the "Instant QR" web application using React + Vite + Tailwind CSS directly in `g:\MY KARNAMEY APPS\Dynamic Qr Code Generater`. We will build this in isolated phases (using Git branches) to ensure a solid and trackable history, with **atomic commits for every single action**.

